            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Our essential oils are widely used in cosmetics, personal care, fragrance, and related industries. We work closely with importers, brands, and manufacturers, providing consistent quality, flexible supply solutions, and export-ready documentation for long-term cooperation.
