<!-- 源头到成品板块 (From Growers to Final Product) -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        
        <!-- 左侧文字内容 -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-custom-main">From Growers to Final Product</h2>
            
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                All high-quality essential oils are rooted in carefully selected botanical raw materials. Different plants have strict requirements for their growing conditions, and climate, soil, water sources, and cultivation methods all directly influence the aromatic composition and quality of the final oil.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                As a manufacturing-focused company, we fully understand the importance of raw material sourcing. We maintain close, long-term relationships with growers and primary suppliers to ensure a stable and reliable supply of botanicals. In some cases, we also introduce carefully selected imported raw materials or essential oils to meet market demand and expand product applications.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 右侧图片区域 (种植源头风格) -->
        <div class="w-full">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
