            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-custom-main">Production & Quality Control System</h2>
            
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                We operate GMP-compliant production workshops in China, equipped with imported automated production equipment and professional sterilization and testing systems. Standardized production lines are used to maintain consistent quality across production batches.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                A structured quality control system is applied throughout the production process, covering raw material incoming inspection, extraction, processing, and final filling, with sampling checks conducted at key stages.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Standardized warehousing facilities are in place, supported by a warehouse management system that helps maintain stable storage conditions and product integrity during storage.
            </p>
